<h2 id="discounts">Automatic Discounts</h2>

<p>Corresponding authors based in the following countries/locations are eligible to receive a 50% discount on APCs* when publishing in a Wiley Open Access journal:</p><br />
<p>*Automatic discounts can only be applied if the corresponding author selects to pay directly or arrange for payment at the payment step during article submission.</p></br>

